            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated paneer</strong> and cook for 5-6 min until golden, turning occasionally for even colouring</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>golden paneer</strong> to a plate – these are your <strong>spiced paneer nuggets</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
