            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p><p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the beans have thickened, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pot and cook for 1 min further or until starting to wilt – these are your <strong>masala saag beans</strong></p>",
