    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spiced paneer nuggets</strong> with the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>masala saag beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
